Permissions & Policies
1) Internet
	- ACCESS_NETWORK_STATE (access network info)
	- ACCESS_WIFI_STATE (access wifi networks)
	- CHANGE_NETWORK_STATE
	- CHANGE_WIFI_MULTICAST_STATE
	- CHANGE_WIFI_STATE
	- INTERNET


2) File System/SMS/Phone Pictures
	- AUTHENTICATE_ACCOUNTS
	- DELETE_PACKAGES
	- INSTALL_PACKAGES
	- GET_ACCOUNTS
	- READ_CALENDAR
	- READ_CONTACTS
	- WRITE_CALENDAR
	- WRITE_CONTACTS
	- WRITE_PROFILE
	- READ_PROFILE
	- READ_SMS
	- WRITE_SMS
	- RECEIVE_MMS
	- RECEIVE_SMS

3) Phone Information
	- MODIFY_PHONE_STATE
	- READ_PHONE_STATE

4) GPS/Camera/Phone Features
	- ACCESS_COARSE_LOCATION (cell-id, wifi)
	- ACCESS_FINE_LOCATION (GPS)
	- ADD_VOICEMAIL
	- CALL_PHONE
	- CALL_PRIVILEGED
	- PROCESS_OUTGOING_CALLS
	- BLUETOOTH
	- BLUETOOTH_ADMIN
	- CAMERA
	- DISABLE_KEYGUARD
	- RECORD_AUDIO
	- SEND_SMS
